lets write the code here 

before going to write we will know the sections present in terraform 

sections present in terraform is 3 sections 1. Provider section 2. Resource section 3. Variable section

[root@TERRAFORM ~]# mkdir pranay ---------------------->
[root@TERRAFORM ~]# cd pranay/ ---------------------->

Now we will do create infrasture by using Provider section & Resource section 

vim provider.tf

provider "aws" {
region =  "us-east-1"
}

:wq

vim resource.tf

resource "aws_instance" "myinstance" {
tags = {
Name = "My-Instance"
Environment = "Dev"
Client = "At&T"
}

ami = "ami-0c3389a4fa5bddaad"
instance_type = "t3.micro"
key_name = "Anjeneyakeypair"
availability_zone = "us-east-1b"
}

:wq

