lifecycle of Terraform is IPAD----------> Terraform init, terraform plan, terraform apply & terraform destroy

Terraform init -------> it downloads the modeules from cloud provider
terraform plan --------> it will give the overview 
terraform apply --------> it will apply the changes on cloud actual action
terraform destroy --------> destroy the resource


